race.comment: ANDI DON'T CARE (11) got the maiden victory out of the way over this track and trip last time out and will have taken a stack of confidence from that breakthrough victory. Winning rider Jones stays on top and is sure to get the run of the race from gate two. Expect another strong showing. METALCRAFT (10) boasts a win over this course and distance and will strip fitter third-up from the spell. Should prove tough to run down. HEY CHARDONNAY (19) resumes here but has revved up for this with a recent trial and can run a big race while fresh. BALTRAY (3) is a bit hit-or-miss but is more than capable enough on his day. Include with the 2kg claim. LANTAU ISLAND (7) best of the rest from the Gollan yard.
